\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
1.
 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy governs the Containment phase of the ECIO incident response lifecycle,
 establishing the Incident Commander's decision framework for containment strategy selection,
 the mandatory evaluation criteria for that selection,
 and the playbooks that guide technical execution for each incident type recognized by the ECIO classification system.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
2.
 Scope
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy applies to all Information Operations Department personnel participating in incident response operations during the containment phase,
 including the IT Director,
 Assistant IT Director,
 Network Administrator,
 Systems Administrator,
 and all technicians operating under Incident Commander authority.
\end_layout

