\series default
 (Annual Policy Review and Maturity Scoring).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Enforcement
\series default
:
 The following conditions constitute specific non-compliance with this policy:
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Failure to document the IC's containment strategy decision — including mode selected and rationale against the three mandatory evaluation criteria — in the work order Notes before execution begins.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Execution of containment configuration actions without IC authorization or without an associated work order in the System of Engagement.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Failure to create catch-up RFC documentation within the window established by 
\series bold
Policy 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
